What is the best app for bike navigation?
text:
Note: I am looking for navigation solutions, planning of bike tours, sightseeing using a bike or bike exercise.

Features I am interested in:

- fastest route

- factor in velocity for different types of road (such as gravel vs paved)

- avoid tracks that are not being cleared in the winter

- avoid dirt tracks when it rains or has rained recently

- factor in uphill and downhill velocity differences - avoid specific roads

- map that shows the route and includes track types

Further features

- availability: Android

- history, save certain goal location

- voice output

Nice to have

- recording

- statistics of the track (or track recording)

- visualisations of track statistics

Ask HN: Expectation that ChatBots have perfect personalities when humans don't?
text:
Humans all have different knowledge sets, experiences, and personalities.

Why do we expect all ChatBots to have a perfect knowledge set and personality?

Lots of conscious humans say horrible things, isn't it expected that some of the ChatBots created will say rude things or have an evil personality?

Just like humans go through therapy and some people are nicer than others, certain ChatBots will win out that align with the desires of the human trainers (whether that is good or bad).

A lot of people seem to be down on LLMs, when we are literally in the first out of the first inning of the baseball game.

Better training, with nicer humans, with better knowledge graphs, and corpus of texts will result in ChatBots indistinguishable from humans (of a given personality and intelligence).

title: Another Blocked Facebook Account
text:
Hello, fellow HN readers,

I don't like it, and probably neither do you, but I have come with a request for help with another blocked Facebook page, as has unfortunately become commonplace.

My case is an account which has been used in my mom's work to administer their special pedagogy center FB page [0]. They have been locked out, presumably due to bad security. The page does not seem to be defaced. The account will be deleted in less than a week. Upon logging in, I am presented with a message that the account has been locked and two buttons. One says "Download my information", which would be satisfactory, but upon clicking on it, a message saying "Download request unsuccessful" comes up. The second button redirects to the help center, where a form can be submitted, but alas, there has been no response.

This is my last shot in the dark, as it probably is for many people who post requests like this. I thank the HN administrators for their consideration of this request and anyone who is able to help me with this.

[0] https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100063644376851

Advice for a “Feedback app for AI” in the making
text:
Hey there,

I am building an app that helps AI applications collect feedback from your users based on specific behaviors and context.What problem we are trying to solve - After talking to a few people who are building tools using AI, it became very clear that they are currently unaware if their users are happy with the outcome generated from the AI. Considering you don't know the input ( what the user will put) & the output ( that the machine will generate).The plan is to give some feedback option to the user when they are interacting within your app and not via email/slack/discord because the context is lost & is time-consuming.

Can you give me some feedback about the features necessary for such an app? Here is the current version: https://productlogz.com/
